resource.http://dev.llgc.org.uk/sas/full_text: Lady Bridget Bertie (nee Wray; 1627-1657) was the daughter of Elizabeth Wray (nee Norris) and Edward Wray. She inherited the family titles and estates on her mother's death in 1645, and married Montague Bertie, second Early of Lindsey, at some time between 1646 and 1653.
